metadata.title: 2002 Groundfish Assessment Survey, Aleutian Islands Region

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS), Alaska Fisheries Science Center (AFSC)

metadata.description: To build a standardized time series of data to assess, describe, and monitor the distribution, abundance, and biological condition of various groundfish and invertebrate stocks that occur in the Aleutian Islands region.
